# üìå Pijii ‚Äì Personal Task Manager

**Pijii** is a full-stack web-based task manager that helps users organize tasks, manage priorities, and schedule deadlines efficiently. Built using Laravel and React via Inertia.js, it offers a smooth, responsive user experience with modern UI components and powerful task/project organization features.

---

## ‚öôÔ∏è Technologies Used

### üñ• Backend
- **Laravel 12** ‚Äì PHP web framework for routing, controllers, and APIs
- **SQLite** ‚Äì Lightweight database for local development

### üíª Frontend
- **React 19** ‚Äì Interactive UI with component-based design
- **Inertia.js** ‚Äì Bridges Laravel backend and React frontend as a single-page app
- **Tailwind CSS 4** ‚Äì Utility-first CSS framework
- **Mantine UI 8** ‚Äì Beautiful, accessible React component library
- **Vite 6** ‚Äì Fast build tool and dev server

### üöÄ Deployment
- **Railway** ‚Äì Hosting and deployment platform for full-stack apps
Here is the link to our app: https://pijii-production.up.railway.app/
---

## üîë Features

- ‚úÖ Task creation, editing, deletion
- üóÇ Project grouping and hierarchy (parent-subproject)
- üè∑ Category grouping for projects
- üìÖ Scheduling with deadlines and reminders
- ‚ö†Ô∏è Priority flag indicators
- üñ±Ô∏è Drag-and-drop interface using pure Tailwind CSS
- üß† Search functionality
- üì§ Archive and restore projects/tasks
- üë§ Auth with user profile editing and account deletion

---

## üõ† Installation Guide

### 1. Required Software

> Install these before proceeding:
- [PHP 8.2+](https://windows.php.net/download/)
- [Composer](https://getcomposer.org/)
- [Node.js 18+](https://nodejs.org/)
- [Git](https://git-scm.com/)
- [VS Code](https://code.visualstudio.com/)

---

### 2. Setup PHP on Windows (if needed)

- Extract downloaded PHP zip
- Copy its path and add to System Environment Variables ‚Üí Path
- Create or edit `php.ini` in the PHP folder: Then **uncomment** these lines (remove `;` at the beginning):


  ```ini
  extension=zip
  extension=fileinfo
  extension=openssl
  extension=pdo_sqlite
  extension=sqlite3


### 3. Clone and Setup Project

# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/your-username/pijii.git
cd pijii

# Install PHP dependencies
composer install

# Install JavaScript dependencies
npm install

# Copy and setup .env
cp .env.example .env
php artisan key:generate

# Run migrations
php artisan migrate

# Storage link
php artisan storage:link

RUN APP LOCALLY

# Start development server
php artisan serve

# In another terminal tab
npm run dev

# In a third tab, start task scheduling (for reminders)
php artisan schedule:work

